<h1>💍 Tourmaline Engagement Rings: A Colorful & Meaningful Alternative to Diamonds</h1>

<p>
Looking for an engagement ring that’s vibrant, full of personality, and rich in symbolic meaning? <strong>Tourmaline engagement rings</strong> are rising stars in the world of alternative bridal jewelry — offering stunning color variety, emotional depth, and ethical appeal for modern couples.
</p>

<h2>What Is Tourmaline? A Stone with Stories</h2>
<p>
Tourmaline is a semi-precious gemstone renowned for its kaleidoscope of colors — from pink and mint green to watermelon and rare Paraiba blue. Unlike traditional diamonds, each tourmaline gem has its own personality, making it the perfect centerpiece for a ring as unique as your story.
</p>

