<p>
Choosing a <strong>tourmaline engagement ring</strong> isn’t just about trends — it’s about wearing something that reflects your story. Whether you’re drawn to pink’s softness, green’s grounding energy, or the boldness of paraiba, this gemstone has a voice — and so do you.
